  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/a1eda9df68a41c1fe1659ca92aac52d9.avif?t=1732008563\" width=600 height=205 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/575e425523e35784cb58800348c9530c.webp?t=1732008563\" width=600 height=47 /></span>Animal memes  such as <strong>Power Hook Dog, Mighty Fox, Magic Squirrel</strong> and more </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >are now become Fighters!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple Controls & Funny Animals & Exciting Battles!!! </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your favorite animal and join the fight!! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players are able to fight through arcade mode become the <strong>King of Animals!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >also allows players to challenge people around the globe online! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/ef7960b011800acdb7127f3814f1d194.webp?t=1732008563\" width=600 height=47 /></span><strong>Only four buttons required!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Fight of Animals, the controls are much easier than most of modern fighting games,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Afraid no more!! with our \"easy combo\" system and simple direction+skill button control, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >allows players perform awesome moves even </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >if you have <strong>NEVER PLAY ANY FIGHTING GAME BEFORE!! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/a4d90b39b4ec04fb594459912383d050.poster.avif?t=1732008563\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/a4d90b39b4ec04fb594459912383d050.webm?t=1732008563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/a4d90b39b4ec04fb594459912383d050.mp4?t=1732008563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/282f7b6449daa053841ec430cdaac4b3.webp?t=1732008563\" width=600 height=47 /></span>With highly synchronized online matching feature, Players are allowed to fight with others from web, Or simply </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >invite your friends from your<strong> Steam friend list </strong>and see who is a better fighter! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/3fb5c5ed5f87a2d9a57b14057b00739d.avif?t=1732008563\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/717d2f5c9186b3bc9194131765207441.webp?t=1732008563\" width=600 height=47 /></span>Each animal (Character) all comes with unique design moves and super!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of curse, each awesome moves all have their advantage and weak spot, avoid smashing the same move</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and find the right timing to smash your opponent!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/84089b4a6d6c06e918cabad16b8e9cd9.poster.avif?t=1732008563\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/84089b4a6d6c06e918cabad16b8e9cd9.webm?t=1732008563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/84089b4a6d6c06e918cabad16b8e9cd9.mp4?t=1732008563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/a1eda9df68a41c1fe1659ca92aac52d9.avif?t=1732008563\" width=600 height=205 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/575e425523e35784cb58800348c9530c.webp?t=1732008563\" width=600 height=47 /></span>Animal memes  such as <strong>Power Hook Dog, Mighty Fox, Magic Squirrel</strong> and more </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >are now become Fighters!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple Controls & Funny Animals & Exciting Battles!!! </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your favorite animal and join the fight!! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players are able to fight through arcade mode become the <strong>King of Animals!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >also allows players to challenge people around the globe online! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160330/extras/ef7960b011800acdb7127f3814f1d194.webp?t=1732008563\" width=600 height=47 /></span><strong>Only four buttons required!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Fight of Animals, the controls are much easier than most of modern fighting games,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Afraid no more!! with our \"easy combo\" system and simple direction+skill button control, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >allows players perform awesome moves even </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >if you have <strong>NEVER PLAY ANY FIGHTING GAME BEFORE!! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop plays